Company Overview:
Nova Cloud Analytics Pvt. Ltd. is Bengaluru based data analytics (SaaS) startup, founded in 2022. It's a technology startup provides cloud-based data analytics solutions for small and medium businesses. The company develops a Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) platform that allows organizations to analyze operational data, generate insights and create business intelligence dashboards. The platform is delivered through a secure web application hosted on public cloud infrastructure.

Technologies referenced in the enviroment:
• Amazon Web Services (EC2, RDS, S3)
• Slack
• Google workspace
• Github
